{"tid":949141,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【東九劈價】滙景花園失守800萬 比上月低位再跌70萬","createTime":"2018-12-20T15:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T23:41:39.000Z","uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c37b5045ab2ce1622908f36ed46d47d883a2c2","tid":949141,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"2018年12月20日 <br />\n【東九劈價】滙景花園失守800萬 比上月低位再跌70萬 <br />\n<br />\n觀塘新盤凱滙低開後，東九龍屋苑劈價停不了。<br />\n<br />\n藍田地鐵站上蓋屋苑滙景花園，兩房造價失守800萬元。消息指3座高層B室，實用面積537方呎，原叫價860萬元，剛減至760萬元成交，呎價14,153元。屋苑對上一宗兩房成交8座低層D室，上月以830萬元成交。今次成交較上月低位跌70萬元，而且高層已平過低層戶。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181220/large/1545308237_ba01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F1545308237_ba01.jpg&h=8d02b630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181220/59052946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59052946&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ddcb49f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59052946&h=38618882\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181220/59052946</a>"},{"pid":"4d8c7127ab133850fff123e7338657223fad239e","tid":949141,"uid":61398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fd2d0a73cd04cba0e1a95bc3513908a2c74ab98","tid":949141,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細路，當年一期果排起樓果陣火燭死過人<br />\n兇樓唔計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁要全個屋苑都唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fe437abed3013b4b372e8b3d29e678d26990f0","tid":949141,"uid":83720,"like"